  - **Duration Decrease**: Possibly due to immediate rejection or processing failure.\n   - **Error Occurrence**: Consistent context canceled errors indicating unavailable service or disruption.\n\n### Hypotheses\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Fronted and RecommendationService calls to ProductCatalog show latency increase from normal averages of ~11,000 ms to anomaly averages above 56,000,000 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Error messages indicating failures to retrieve specific products during order placement.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nBased on these observations, the root cause of the anomalies seems linked to delays and failures in the `ProductCatalogService` along with impacted order processing by `CheckoutService`.", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"The server_error_ratio increased significantly, indicating potential server-side issues. This is supported by a change in server_error_ratio from normal to fault conditions.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=32.46, p99_fault=57.7\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"A noticeable increase in server_error_ratio and error_ratio occurred, suggesting backend processing issues causing higher errors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: normal_median=0.0, fault_median=36.93, p99_fault=50.0; error_ratio: no